      <title>中日总理赴首尔举行2019年以来首次会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国、日本和韩国将举行自 2019 年以来的首次三方峰会，东京和首尔在安全和半导体生产等问题上与美国走得更近，向北京施压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言在加密货币上诉中援助被定罪的“丝绸之路”创始人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/trump-vows-to-aid-convicted-silk-road-founder-in-crypto-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普呼吁对丝绸之路在线市场创始人罗斯·乌布利希进行减刑，试图将自己定位为自由意志选民支持加密货币的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/trump-vows-to-aid-convicted-silk-road-founder-in-crypto-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于莫迪的民意调查目标存疑，印度市场准备迎接抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-s-markets-brace-for-selloff-if-modi-bjp-disappoints-at-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在民意调查中赢得微弱多数，印度蓬勃发展的市场将面临抛售的风险，这将危及他更广泛改革的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-s-markets-brace-for-selloff-if-modi-bjp-disappoints-at-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
